<item>
            <title>[LU-878] Test failure on test suite sanityn, subtest test_40b</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-878</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;sanityn 40b is checking pdirops, but it seems once OBD_FAIL_MDS_PDO_LOCK is set, it will only wait 10 seconds to timeout, if the test cannot finish in 10 seconds, it will fail.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/e73821d4-16be-11e1-9d03-52540025f9af&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/e73821d4-16be-11e1-9d03-52540025f9af&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The sub-test test_40b failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;unlink is blocked&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;</description>
